<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Smart</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/CEhaker.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/Photos/smart_academy-updated.png">
    <style>
        .video-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 56.25%;
            height: 0;
            margin: 20px auto;
            max-width: 90%;
        }
        .video-wrapper iframe {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <img class="logo-img" src="/Photos/smart_academy-updated.png" alt="logo" onclick="window.location.href='/home'"> 
        <h2>Certified Ethical Hacker</h2>
    </header>

    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/home">Home</a>
            <a href="/courses">Courses</a>
            <a href="/aboutUs">About Us</a>
            <a href="/contactUs">Contact</a>
            <%- include('partials/cart') %>
        </div>

        <div class="nav-auth">
            <% if (user) { %>
                <% if (user.isAdmin) { %>
                    <a href="admin/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary me-2">Dashboard</a>
                <% } %>
                <button id="logoutBtn">Logout</button>
            <% } else { %>
                <a href="/signlog" class="auth-btn">Sign Up</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div id="cartModal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close">&times;</span>
            <h2 class="modalTitle">Shopping Cart</h2>
            <div id="cartItems"></div>
            <div class="cart-total">
                <strong>Total: </strong>
                <span id="cartTotal">$0</span>
            </div>
            <button id="checkoutBtn" class="checkout-btn">
                Proceed to Checkout
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="course-banner">
        <img src="/Photos/cyber-hacker.jpg" alt="Certified Ethical Hacker" class="course-image">
    </div>

    <!-- Embedded YouTube Video -->
    <div class="video-wrapper">
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OymIyNMe9aE" title="Certified Ethical Hacker Overview" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>

    <div class="course-content">
        <section class="overview">
            <h2>Course Overview</h2>
            <p>Master the art of ethical hacking and become a certified security professional. This comprehensive course teaches you advanced penetration testing techniques, vulnerability assessment, and security strategies used by ethical hackers to protect organizations from cyber threats.</p>
            <div class="course-actions">
                <button class="add-to-cart" data-course="ceh" data-price="999">
                    <i class="fas fa-cart-plus"></i>
                    Add to Cart - $120
                </button>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="what-you-learn">
            <h2>What You Will Learn</h2>
            <div class="learning-points">
                <ul>
                    <li>Advanced penetration testing methodologies</li>
                    <li>Network and system hacking techniques</li>
                    <li>Web application security testing</li>
                    <li>Malware analysis and reverse engineering</li>
                    <li>Social engineering and countermeasures</li>
                    <li>Cloud computing security</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="Curriculum">
            <h2>Course Curriculum</h2>
            <div class="module-list">
                <div class="module">
                    <h3>Module 1: Introduction to Ethical Hacking</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Understanding Ethical Hacking</li>
                        <li>Information Security Controls</li>
                        <li>Penetration Testing Methodology</li>
                        <li>Legal and Ethical Aspects</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="module">
                    <h3>Module 2: Reconnaissance and Footprinting</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Information Gathering Techniques</li>
                        <li>Network Scanning</li>
                        <li>Vulnerability Analysis</li>
                        <li>OSINT Tools and Techniques</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="module">
                    <h3>Module 3: System Hacking</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Password Cracking Techniques</li>
                        <li>Privilege Escalation</li>
                        <li>Maintaining Access</li>
                        <li>Covering Tracks</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="requirements">
            <h2>Prerequisites</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Strong understanding of networking concepts</li>
                <li>Basic knowledge of Linux and Windows operating systems</li>
                <li>Familiarity with command-line interfaces</li>
                <li>Understanding of basic security concepts</li>
                <li>Programming/scripting knowledge is beneficial</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/CEhaker.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/logOut.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
